# Profit Or Loss Insurance Loss Recognition Amount

## identifier
de5555

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, for loss recognition and/or loss reversal as defined in the relevant prudential standards. This relates to an actuarial method for valuing policy liabilities.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.Insurance.LossRecognition.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.04
- period=duration
